description: The Amazon was the 8th ranked wrestler of the second season. She is big, strong, and has solid wrestling skills. She is the only opponent the Pirate has wrestled heavier then her. However, it didn’t matter. The Pirate shows why she was last season’s Champion. The only questions that remain are: Did the Amazon score, and how hard did she get fucked?
title: The Pirate (0-0) vs. The Amazon (0-0)
